resultset.statement: select building_id, name, (select nominative from geo_cities as gc where b.city_id = gc.city_id) as city, address, class, state, developer_offer from buildings as b where region_id = 10 and is_active = 'yes' and is_risky = 'no' and building_type = 'new_building' order by building_id asc
